name: Tonight
detailedForecast: A chance of snow before 10pm, then a chance of snow and patchy fog between 10pm and 11pm, then patchy fog and a chance of rain and snow between 11pm and 4am. Mostly cloudy. Low around 25, with temperatures rising to around 34 overnight. Southwest wind around 9 mph. Chance of precipitation is 50%. New snow accumulation of less than one inch possible.
